OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSaturday post should stay, 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgovernment says            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has said it would not   
OL,6, support Royal Mail scrapping post      
OL,7, deliveries on Saturdays.               
OL,9,FThe company has said it would like     
OL,10,Fdeliveries from Monday to Friday only. 
OL,12,FBut Downing Street said the government 
OL,13,F"would not countenance" such a move, as
OL,14,Fa review by regulator Ofcom is looking 
OL,15,Finto the future of the postal service. 
OL,17,F"The PM's strong view is that Saturday 
OL,18,Fdeliveries provide flexibility and     
OL,19,Fconvenience," said Rishi Sunak's       
OL,20,Fspokesperson on Monday.                
